    "These trees are then used as an ensemble forming a random forest (RF) to improve the predictive performance.",
    "Morphocluster (Schröder et al. 2020) utilizes a semi-automated iterative approach and hierarchical density-based HDBSCAN* (Campello et al. 2015) for plankton image data analysis.",
    "To compute image features for the clustering a CNN trained with UVP5/EcoTaxa dataset in a supervised manner was used.",
    "The method works iteratively in a semi-automated manner so that clusters are validated by an expert.",
    "An improved version of Morphocluster was presented by Schröder and Kiko (2022)."
